    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "July 21, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "CORDED 62-83894-64",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "-67 [REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Hicksville, Long Island, New York",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Dear [REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "I wish to acknowledge receipt of your letter and enclosure dated",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "July 10, 1947.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "I have instructed the Special Agent in Charge of our New York Office",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "to have a Special Agent call upon you for the purpose of obtaining further",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "information in connection with this matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Your interest in calling this information to my attention is indeed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "appreciated.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "John Edgar Hoover",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Director",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "cc - New York (With [unclear]). There is no identifiable information in the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "files of the Bureau concerning the writer of this letter. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "decoding of the message on the newspaper clipping was referred",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "to the Laboratory, who subsequently advised that the writer's",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "decoding was substantially correct. There is being set forth",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "below the results of the Laboratory's decoding:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "\"TIRED OF HUMAN NONSENSE WE AWAIT ATOMIC",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "WAR DISRUPTING ORDER SOLAR SYSTEM SO SENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "FLYING DISKS AND WILL SET UP WORLD ORDER",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "UNDER MARTIAN'S LATE THIS YEAR\".",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "The New York Office should interview the writer of this letter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "to ascertain from what newspaper the clipping in question was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "obtained. Thereafter, contact should be made with this newspaper",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "to ascertain the identity of the person who sent in the coded",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "message. This individual must be thoroughly interrogated to obtain",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "all possible information surrounding the alleged receipt of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "coded message. The Bureau should be promptly advised of the results",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "of these inquiries.)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
